(3) U.S. Pat. No. 6,280,468 entitled “SCLERAL PROSTHESIS FOR TREATMENT OF PRESBYOPIAAND OTHER EYE DISORDERS” issued Aug. 28, 2001;

(4) U.S. Pat. No. 5, 465,737 entitled “TREATMENT OF PRESBYOPIA AND OTHER EYE DISORDERS” issued on Nov. 14, 1995;

