(6) U.S. Pat. No. 5,503,165 entitled “TREATMENT OF PRESBYOPIA AND OTHER EYE DISORDERS” issued on Apr. 2, 1996;

(7) U.S. Pat. No. 5,529,076 entitled “TREATMENT OF PRESBYOPIA AND OTHER EYE DISORDERS” issued on Jun. 25, 1996;

